Package com.camerontec.catalys.util.data

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IBindable<T>
    Interface defining a general contract for binding an instance of an object to another object.
    IDoubleToDecimalConverter
    The Catalys API does not accept double values, conversions should be performed on the client side.
    IFIXBytesImportable
    Interface to be implemented by classes capable of importing raw FIX formatted bytes.
    ITagOrderingRegistry
    Stores tag order information used by OrderedTagValues.
    ITagValue
    Holds an int tag and an IValue object.
    ITagValueIterableFromTag<I extends Iterator<ITagValue>>
    Interface defining iteration over an underlying sequence of ITagValues.
    ITagValueIteratorBindable<I extends Iterator<ITagValue>>
    Interface to be implemented by all ITagValue collections capable of providing iteration with reusable java.util.Iterators.
    ITagValues
    Collection of ITagValue objects.
    ITagValuesListener
    Defines an interface for classes which wish to listen for changes on an ITagValues.
    ITagValuesReadable
    Read only interface to an ITagValues collection.
    IValue
    Wrapper for values of different type.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractTagOrderingRegistry
    Base class for AbstractTagOrderingRegistry which computes tagPaths given an ordering.
    AbstractTagValues
    This class provides a skeletal implementation of the ITagValues interface to minimize the effort required to implement this interface backed by a collection of ITagValue objects.
    AbstractTagValuesListIterator<T>
    Base class for all AbstractTagValues iterator implementations.
    AbstractTagValuesReadable
    This class provides a skeletal implementation of the ITagValuesReadable interface to minimize the effort required to implement this interface backed by a collection of ITagValue objects.
    Decimal
    Representation of a floating point number as an int exponent and long mantissa.
    DefaultDoubleToDecimalConverter
    A double to decimal converter that refuses to perform any conversions.
    ITagValueUtilities
    Some useful utilities which act on ITagValues objects.
    LegacyDoubleToDecimalConverter
    Performs double to decimal conversion using the legacy Catalys approach.
    NameValue
    General purpose name/value pair.
    OrderedTagValues
    ITagValues whose elements are maintained in a strict order according to their tags.
    StandardTagValue
    Standard implementation of ITagValue.
    StandardValue
    Standard implementation of IValue
    TagValuesAsArray
    ITagValues implemented as an extensible array.
    TagValuesAsArrayIterator
    Concrete iterator for ITagValue array based storage.
    TagValuesAsIndexedByteArray
    ITagValues implemented as a byte array in FIX format (tag=value<soh>) with an index to entries in the byte array.
    TagValuesAsIndexedList
    ITagValues implemented as a LinkedList with an index by tag number to entries in the list.
    TagValuesAsList
    ITagValues implemented as an ArrayList.
    TagValuesAsListIterator
    Concrete iterator for ITagValue java.util.List storage.
    TagValuesAsOrderedIndexedList Deprecated
    TagValuesSerializationUtil
    Utilities for serialization.
    UtilityITagValues
    Some useful utilities which act on ITagValues objects.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    BadDataException  
    ConversionException
    Exception thrown when an attempt to conversion one type of data to another type fails - for example, a String to an int.
    MissingDataException
